            "value": "<p>Granted by @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Clinging Shadows Stance]{Clinging Shadows Stance}</p>\n<p>You adopt the stance of clinging shadows. You can make shadow grasp @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Strike]{Strikes}. These deal 1d4 negative damage; are in the brawling group; and have the agile, grapple, reach, and unarmed traits.</p>\n<p>While in the clinging shadows stance, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Athletics checks to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Grapple]{Grapple}, and to the DC for creatures to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Escape]{Escape} from you.</p>"
